(14, 'Des grandes banques en France à l’élevage des porcs: le success-story d’une fermière congolaise', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555555; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12.8px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">lenne Mouangou est rentr&eacute;e dans son Congo Brazzaville natal s</span></strong><strong style=\"font-size: 12.8px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">&rsquo;</span></strong><strong style=\"font-size: 12.8px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">investir dans l</span></strong><strong style=\"font-size: 12.8px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">&rsquo;</span></strong><strong style=\"font-size: 12.8px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">&eacute;levage. Elle est pass&eacute;e de cinq &agrave; plus de 200 porcs.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555555; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">A 38 ans, Clenne Mouangou est une &eacute;leveuse de porcs. La fondatrice de&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black;\">CMAgrobusiness, une entreprise agroalimentaire, est une femme&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black;\">&laquo;&nbsp;</span><em><span style=\"color: black;\">D</span></em><em><span style=\"color: black;\">&eacute;ter</span></em><em><span style=\"color: black;\">min</span></em><em><span style=\"color: black;\">&eacute;e</span></em><span style=\"color: black;\">&raquo;</span><span style=\"color: black;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: black;\">&laquo;&nbsp;</span><em><span style=\"color: black;\">ambitieuse&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"color: black;\">&raquo;</span><span style=\"color: black;\">,&nbsp;</span><span sty